						               													<description>Fire the Cannons! is a tile laying game where players compete to build the largest castle, while strategically using cannon fire to ruins their opponents' castles. Its a Euro-style game, no die rolling for mechanic resolution. Playing the tiles builds your castle, situates the cannons, and when a sufficient number of flag-tiles are played, fires the cannons.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Starting with the player holding the cannon and proceeding clockwise, each player should take one territory&amp;#10;tile from the face-up pile in the center of the board and add it next to another tile in their kingdom.&amp;#10;The tile may be rotated when being placed.&amp;#10;Only when an area is completely enclosed by walls, however, is it considered &amp;ldquo;secured&amp;rdquo;. If an area has one or more gaps, it is considered &amp;ldquo;under siege&amp;rdquo; until all of the gaps are filled.&amp;#10;Each tile will generally have one or more special symbols on the tile. Adding three commander (red flag) symbols to one&amp;rsquo;s kingdom will trigger a round of attack. The player will score during this time as well.&amp;#10;At the end of the round, refill the center play area with new tiles from the territory tile stack&amp;#10;The player with the highest score when no tiles remain in the center of the play area wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Is freely available from http://www.vbasementgames.com/ after you create an account.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
